<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10094315>
    dc:description "FIGURE 41. Xenorthrius perroti: (A) Tegmen in ventral view, (B) phallus in ventral view, (C) tip of aedeagus in lateral view, (D) spicular fork, (E) male pygidium, (F) male ventrite 6 and distribution map." ;
